  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="SV">Insats 11736: Under rutin granskning av planenliga finansrapporter 2020, gjordes flera markeringar g&#xE4;llande felaktiga budget ber&#xE4;kningar och &#xE4;ndringar samt oegentliga f&#xF6;rklaringar p&#xE5; flera st&#xE4;llen i finansredovisningen. 
D&#xE4;rf&#xF6;r besl&#xF6;t Sida att upphandla en egen riktade revision f&#xF6;r att n&#xE5; klarg&#xF6;rande, resulterande i denna insats 15121.</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The purpose of this assignment is to:
Establish facts to prove, or disprove, any misuse of funds, fraud, conflict of interests, undue influence, misinformation and mismanagement, in contravention of sound financial management, the requirements in the 
 contribution agreement, and/or partners&apos; policies and procedures concerning recruitment, use of consultants, staff and salary costs (including bonuses and benefits), and budgeting for 2019 and 2020.</narrative>
  </description>
